## Hard rules

âťŚ **NIE pushuj force** bez explicit user request (lub destroys upstream history)
âťŚ **NIE amend published commits** (use new commits instead)
âťŚ **NIE skip hooks** (`--no-verify`) bez user request
âťŚ **NIE commit files which contain secrets** (`.env`, credentials.json, etc.) â€” check `.gitignore` first
âťŚ **NIE commit pre-implementation files w masowy commit** â€” incremental discovery > big bang

